Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.34,0:00:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told you before,\Nbut I'll tell you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.51,0:00:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Our MP would never\Nbe involved with a prostitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.59,0:00:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, he has no connection
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to that woman's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.06,0:00:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep pestering me,\NI'll do what I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to sue me for slander?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, a secretary like you\Nwould not do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.94,0:00:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be bad for MP Boltzmann\Nto be linked to this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.57,0:00:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you threatening me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.62,0:00:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.83,0:00:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a tough nut to crack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Typical for a prominent MP's secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we just need one final push.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.13,0:02:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,MP Boltzmann is such a major politician.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think he would be involved\Nwith that prostitute?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The victim is not an ordinary prostitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She's linked to several figures\Nin the political and financial worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But only one person saw her
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.36,0:02:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,at the hotel Boltzmann stayed at.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we have enough information\Nto prove there's anything between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the progress\Nof her client list's decoding?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The floppy disk has multiple passwords,\Nso it's taking some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.58,0:02:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me do it. Give me the floppy disk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… But aren't you busy\Nwith other cases?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind. Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Um… I've been meaning to ask you…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you ever sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that have to do with the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.77,0:03:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an irrational question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.69,0:03:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When are you going to tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't matter when we tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He never listens to us anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's still better to tell him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your voice down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That's rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.26,0:03:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,GERMAN FEDERAL\NCRIMINAL POLICE OFFICE (BKA)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you're still looking\Nat the murder of that prostitute
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and her relationship with MP Boltzmann.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! A big problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Big shots from the Ministry\Nof the Interior are pressuring us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then please take care of it\Nas you usually do, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I cannot help you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you will manage something anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lunge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What if this investigation\Nturns out to be a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You have already built up\Na distinguished career.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to work\Nso aggressively on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it all in the name of justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Work? Justice?\NI'm not interested in either of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I am only interested in the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge, someone is here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I have decoded the password\Nof the client list.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can convert them to real names.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Um… Anyway. She's here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman Eva Heinemann--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:05:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just come in here like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ever going to arrest Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.14,0:05:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You have been drinking quite a lot again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I not drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,About Dr. Tenma…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-I consider his case solved.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He said it was all done\Nby some man called Johan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but that "Johan" is actually\Nanother personality inside of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though that case may seem\Nunreasonable at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,it can be solved rationally if you\Nthink about it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We just have to wait for the police\Nacross the country to catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying your job is done\Nonce the arrest warrant is put out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I have many things I need to ask him\Nwhen I see him, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma is a very intriguing man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there are many cases I need\Nto solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They are piled up high on my desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you so persistent?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you many times.\NThe MP has an alibi that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,An alibi? Indeed.\NThat was the work of a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you implying that the MP hired\Na professional to kill her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I decoded the victim's client list.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The MP's name was in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if his name was on it?\NWhat would be his motive to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's as far as we have got.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of this. Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So that evidence was still not enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you familiar\Nwith the Schellhorn Publishing Company?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They publish books exposing\Nscandals of famous people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow they make a living off it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The way they conduct their business\Nis rather unscrupulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:07:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They hire indecent women to develop\Nrelationships with famous people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they have the women\Nwrite down the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be more cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like checkmate earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That secretary was speechless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised myself to see him\Nnever taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if he's superhuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Superhuman…\NMaybe he's not human after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right. It'd be checkmate\Nif I make that move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't interrupt someone's game--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't waste your energy on a stupid game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The president of that publishing company
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,spit everything out after just\Na little threatening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-Get the preliminary memo.\N-Y… Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that prostitute's memo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Every little detail has been written down,\Nabout her secret affair with a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The man's name is not known,\Nexcept for the initial "B."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Schellhorn Publishing Company
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,made a contract with her\Nto publish her life story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever made contact\Nwith a man called Janker?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That man is a professional assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the hell out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We are moving out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, I'm sure you don't\Neven know I'm pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you moving in with the man\Nwho knocked you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm moving out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no idea I have a lover, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mintag, Boltzmann's secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I will tell you everything.\NPlease come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going out. We'll talk when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In… Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:09:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the fuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The secretary killed himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"MP Boltzmann is innocent."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The secretary left this note\Nbefore he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunge, this case will be passed\Nto Inspector Kaminski,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.31,0:10:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as the cases for Reinkene Park and\Nthe murder of Garland Company's president.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what will I be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing left
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:10:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,for you to do anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I only have you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Inspector. You have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that woman Eva Heinemann again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.10,0:12:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a good time, Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When can I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.57,0:12:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose… I will come by\Nafter my next business trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to let you go back\Nto your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably won't come back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've put my handkerchief soaked\Nwith my perfume in your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cheap man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you staring at me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you wondering why I always bring\Ndifferent men into my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You wish you could be\Nlike them, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I was just…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I love this garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel I can forget all the bad things\Njust by looking at this garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be planting mimosas here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there,\NI will make an arch with roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In summer, it will be beautiful…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps a man like you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you confident that\Nyou can make me happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you listening to me? Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-Daddy!\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… How is daddy's cooking today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't even listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why mom left you for another man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Coletta…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have someone I like…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no. Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's dinner is not good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Not bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a gardener,\Nbut I'm asking you to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All my other servants left me, complaining\Nthat they wanted more free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anything I can help with,\Nplease just ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How about dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you nervous or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… I'm not comfortable\Nin these expensive places.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to be the kind\Nof man worthy of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to be confident\Neverywhere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like when you work in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Y… Yes. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.04,0:15:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm in the garden,\NI do have confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When the garden is shaped up\Nin the way I planned, I'm so happy…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happiest when I'm in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who likes gardens can't be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that you like\Nthat garden as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying I'm a good person?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's just…\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well… You look so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you lonely as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… Sorry. My daughter will worry, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost Christmas, Coletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Santa Claus better not push\Nhimself too hard this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you don't have to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A Christmas party with\Njust the two of us is just sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry too much about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, maybe it won't be just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That man ruined my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So… Sorry! I'm just cleaning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Kenzo Tenma, my ex-fiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're drinking this early again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I not drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I just went to the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to see Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That man! He was worthless,\Nand he dared to turn me away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When are they going to arrest Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The BKA? Arrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That man killed my father and ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he was falsely accused,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but who was he kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the daughter of the big hospital's\Ndirector, and my future was all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My three failed marriages\Nare his fault, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.69,0:17:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"It was all Johan's doing." No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this!\NThis is Johan with my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think such a child\Ncan kill my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma is saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just his silly excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:18:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you give this photo to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be important evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Tenma who did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Inspector Lunge said.\NTenma has multiple personalities!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why do you still have\Nhis photos displayed like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep in your heart,\Nyou still don't think Tenma is the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And you still think of Tenma…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you watch too many soap operas?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He was just the man who was\Nmost worthy of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He was an elite neurosurgeon\Nwho everyone called a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He held a high status.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And more than anything,\Nthis man never talked back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He listened to all my selfish requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Yes, Yes, Yes!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.51,0:18:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a man who said "yes" to everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That man was supposed to make\Nme the happiest woman in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I… be a substitute for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can make the garden for you\Nfor the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as it can give you peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get carried away\Njust because I slept with you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just someone I used to kill time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just messing around with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get the wrong idea, you silly man.\NWho do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You… You are really a lonely person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I will have a party with my daughter\Nat my house on Christmas Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd like, please come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! All this food looks amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you make it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I can't promise\Nit'll all taste good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this too much\Nfor just the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy is coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Coletta…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch… Charlotte?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What mimosas? Roses?\NWhat's this beautiful garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The mansion\Nof the former director of a big hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll burn them all! All of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.33,0:22:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, you have decided to hear me out.\NInspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I just happen to have time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.34,0:22:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This man is all I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot be happy until this man\Nstops breathing.
